                        src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-2.png"
                        alt="image"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="blog-multi-img">
                      <img
                        src="/assets/images/appeals/masjid-3.png"
                        alt="image"
                      />
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">How Your Iftar Donation Makes a Difference

                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                        Each Iftar Food Pack distributed by CRF is carefully prepared to meet the dietary needs of fasting individuals. The contents typically include staple items such as rice, lentils, dates, flour, sugar, and cooking oil, ensuring that families can prepare wholesome meals throughout Ramadan. These food packs are designed to provide essential nutrients and sustain families for several days.

                    </p>
                    <ul class="bullet-list">
                        <li class="list">
                            A single donation can feed an entire family for a week.


                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                            Families no longer have to worry about sourcing their next meal.


                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                            Parents can focus on spiritual practices without the burden of hunger.


                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                            Children can experience the joy of Ramadan with a nutritious Iftar, Creating a sense of stability and joy.


                        </li>
                      </ul>

                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">Donate Iftar Through CRF's Trusted Appeal
                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                        At Care and Relief (CRF), we prioritize 100% transparency and trust. Our donors are at the heart of everything we do, and we ensure that every contribution reaches those in genuine need. With over a decade of experience in Ramadan initiatives, CRF has established efficient processes to distribute Iftar Food Packages to vulnerable communities worldwide.
                        <br><br>
                        Making an Iftar Donation is simple and secure. Here's how you can contribute:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="bullet-list">
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Online Donations:</span>
                           Visit our official website and select the “Donate Iftar” option to make a secure online payment.


                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Bank Transfers:</span>
                           Transfer your contribution directly to our designated account.

                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Community Campaigns:</span>
                           Join our local fundraising efforts to amplify your impact.


                        </li>
                      
                      </ul>
<p class="pera">
    Your support enables us to plan and distribute food packs efficiently, ensuring no family is left behind. By partnering with CRF, you become a part of a trusted initiative that brings hope and sustenance to those in need during Ramadan.

</p>
                

                    <div class="divider"></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="donation-content">
                    <h4 class="title">Why Choose CRF for Iftar Food Packages?

                    </h4>
                    <p class="pera">
                        Care and Relief (CRF) has built a reputation for reliability, compassion, and efficiency. Here's why donors trust us to deliver Iftar Food Packs:

                    </p>
                    <ul class="bullet-list">
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Experience and Expertise:</span>
                           With over 10 years of Ramadan initiatives, we have developed a deep understanding of community needs and logistical planning.



                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Transparency:</span>
                           We provide regular updates and reports to our donors, showcasing how their contributions are utilized.

                        </li>
                        <li class="list">
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Commitment to Impact:</span>
                           Our goal is to maximize the impact of every donation, ensuring that each food pack reaches those who need it most.


                        </li>
                      
                      </ul>
<p class="pera">
    When you choose CRF, you choose an organization that values your trust and works tirelessly to uphold it. We understand the spiritual significance of Ramadan and strive to make your contribution a source of blessings for you and those you support.


</p>
                

                  </div>
              
                </div>
                <!-- blog info -->
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <style>
        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
          #video {
            height: 300px;
          }
        }
      </style>
    </section>
    <!-- Faq section started -->
    <section class="question-area section-padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col my-auto">
            <!-- Section Tittle -->
            <div class="section-tittle mb-50" style="text-align: center;">
              <h2 class="title font-700">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
              <p class="pera">
                When deciding which charity to donate to, it's important to do
                your search and find one that aligns with your values and
                interests.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button"
