                    Each pack contains essential staples including dates, juice, rice, Yogurt, Bread, and fruits to break the fast in Ramadan.


                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed additional-styles"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="collapseTwo"
                  >
                  How does the Care & Relief Foundation distribute Iftar food packs?
                </button>
                </h2>
