                    The Care & Relief Foundation delivers Iftar food packs to families in need across the UK, through volunteers and local centers, based on community assessments.


                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed additional-styles"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="collapseThree"
                    >Can people from outside UK contribute to the Care & relief Foundation's iftar food pack program?

                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="collapseThree"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Yes, people outside the UK can contribute to the Iftar food pack program via our website. We accept international donations, which are used to purchase food for distribution in the UK.


                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed additional-styles"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#collapseFour"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="collapseFour"
                    >How long does an Iftar food pack last?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="collapseFour"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    An Iftar food pack is designed to provide enough iftar food for a family for the entire month of Ramadan, ensuring they have sufficient meals for Iftar each day.
                    

                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                  <button
                    class="accordion-button collapsed additional-styles"
                    type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                    data-bs-target="#collapseFive"
                    aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-controls="collapseFive"
                    >What steps does the Care & Relief Foundation take to ensure the quality and safety of the Iftar food packs?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div
                  id="collapseFive"
                  class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                  aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                  data-bs-parent="#accordionExample"
                >
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    The Care & Relief Foundation follows strict food safety guidelines, sourcing fresh, high-quality ingredients from trusted suppliers. Each pack is carefully prepared and packaged to ensure the safety and freshness of the items.


                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main></Layout
